methods.parse:
Attempt to process the expression using the configured
factories

:param expression: (java.lang.String) - the expression to parse
:param args: java.lang.Object...
:return: (ExpressionParser.TYPE) The result of the parsing
methods.registerFactory:
Add an expression factory to the list of possible parsers for an expression.

:param expressionFactory: (io.deephaven.db.tables.utils.ExpressionFactory<ExpressionParser.TYPE>) - the factory

text:
A parser that will try a set of ExpressionFactorys and attempt to parse the expression until one of them
 succeeds.
